      "rationale": "Only one test condition (5 mm/min, 22 degC) was employed, consistent with ASTM F1717. Rate-independence of Ti-6Al-4V at quasi-static loading rates is well-supported by published literature (Donachie 2000; ASTM F136 data). The operating envelope explicitly bounds the model to this single test condition, so the limitation is acknowledged and scoped. This factor is below required level 3 but accepted given medium model risk and the explicit operating envelope constraint. Required level 3; achieved level 2."
